## Code Blocks

```
Plain code block
with multiple lines
```

```javascript
// JavaScript code block
function hello() {
    console.log("Hello, World!");
}
```

```python #
# Python with line numbers
def greet(name):
    print(f"Hello, {name}!")
```

```php #=10
// PHP starting at line 10
<?php
echo "Hello from PHP";
```

