## Inline Formatting

This is *strong* text.

This is _emphasized_ text.

This is `inline code`.

This is {=highlighted=} text.

This is {+inserted+} text.

This is {-deleted-} text.

This is ^superscript^ text.

This is ~subscript~ text.

This is {^braced superscript^} text.

This is {~braced subscript~} text.

---

## Spans with Attributes

[This is a span]{.highlight}

[Span with ID]{#my-id}

[Span with multiple]{.class1 .class2 #span-id key="value"}

