---

## Edge Cases

Empty emphasis: __ (should not match)

Empty strong: ** (should not match)

Underscore_in_middle_of_word (should not match)

Asterisk*in*word (should not match)

URL with special chars: <https://example.com/path?query=value&other=123>

Code with backticks: `` `code with backtick` ``

Nested brackets: [[nested]] and [outer [inner] outer]

